        time when your information is collected whether certain data is compulsory and the consequences of the failure to
        provide such data.
We collect the following personal data from and about you.
Account information (e.g., nickname, avatar, your third-party account information, e.g., your Facebook account, Google account);
Content information generated when you communicate with us;
Information we collect automatically from you including internet or other electronic network activity information : your
